SUMMARY:CommUnion: Tilt Arcade Bar Social
DESCRIPTION:Wilderness Union Toronto - Outdoor Adventure and Hiking Club\n
 **Please note the only way to register for this adventure is on [our websi
 te.](https://www.wildernessunion.com/adventures/communion-tilt)**\n\n***Ba
 ck again with another social for the homies as we spring into the new seas
 on. This time\, we’re taking over Tilt Arcade Bar in Toronto.***\nWhat y
 ou can expect:\n\n* A great time with new and old friends alike\n* Gamecub
 e consoles so you can finally prove to yourself (and your family) that you
 r sibling was clearly cheating growing up and that you’re not actually t
 hat bad at Mario Kart afterall!!\n* Isaac trying to play dance dance revol
 ution (a must see)\n* Drink tickets for the big winners\n* Loads of food a
 nd drink options\n\nThis spot is super rad because they have tons of amazi
 ng games that you can play as much as you want. They also have good drinks
  (alc & non alc) and some bar food to keep you locked and loaded (figurati
 vely speaking\, of course).\n\nThe price of your ticket gets you access in
 to the venue. Wilderness Union will also be providing a limited amount of 
 food and drink for attendees.\n\nCommUnion is the new name for Wilderness 
 Union's social series. This is a members-only event but you are welcome to
  bring guests!\n\n**Whether you’re new to the community or have been wit
 h us since day 1\, come join in on a great night out! This one should be a
  ton of fun!**\n\n**Highlights**\nUnlimited Arcade Games. Good People. Spr
 ing Vibes.\n\n**Event cost: $10+HST. Register [here.](https://www.wilderne
 ssunion.com/adventures/communion-tilt)**\n\n**About Wilderness Union**\nWi
 lderness Union is deliberate about building an outdoors community that con
 nects you to the life-changing magic of the outdoors and helps you find yo
 ur people.\n\nMembers range from 20-40 years old. The group is a mix of GT
 A locals and newcomers to Toronto from within Canada and abroad.\n\nAttend
 ance numbers on Meetup don't reflect our actual event attendance - we typi
 cally have 15-20 community members at each event. Large enough that there'
 s someone new to meet but small enough that it's not overwhelming!\n\n***L
 earn more at our website [www.wildernessunion.com](https://www.wildernessu
 nion.com/)***
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/wildernessunion/events/314152891/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260406T200012Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260406T200012Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
