SUMMARY:Hilton Falls Mega Hike
DESCRIPTION:Wilderness Union Toronto - Outdoor Adventure and Hiking Club\n
 **Please note the only way to register for this adventure is on [our websi
 te.](https://www.wildernessunion.com/adventures/hilton-falls-mega-hike)**\
 n\n**Join us for this half-marathon spring challenge as we trek a full 21 
 km through the rugged heart of the Hilton Falls trail system.**\n\nWe are 
 heading out to the Milton area to test our endurance amidst Ontario’s be
 autiful scenery. We’ll navigate varied terrain under towering pines that
  define this UNESCO World Biosphere Reserve.\n\nThe air should be crisp an
 d the forest floor will be waking up with the first signs of spring. You c
 an expect a stop at the iconic waterfall and old mill along the way\, a un
 ique feature of this conservation area.\n\nThe day is designed for those w
 ho want to push their endurance while surrounded by a crew of supportive\,
  like-minded adventurers. Please consider your fitness level when register
 ing for this adventure\, as it will be challenging and fast paced.\n\n**Hi
 ghlights**\n**Incredible views:** We will trek along the ridges of the Nia
 gara escarpment\, giving us shimmering views of the horizon and the valley
  below.\n**Half Marathon Hike:** Covering 21 km is the perfect challenge f
 or those looking to level up their endurance with a supportive group.\n**C
 elebratory Drinks:** We’ll go for an (optional) celebration once the hik
 e is done to toast our success with the crew.\n\n**Event cost: $60+HST - o
 ptional transport available.**\n**Register [here.](https://www.wildernessu
 nion.com/adventures/hilton-falls-mega-hike)**\n\n**About Wilderness Union*
 *\nWilderness Union is deliberate about building an outdoors community tha
 t connects you to the life-changing magic of the outdoors and helps you fi
 nd your people.\n\nMembers range from 20-40 years old. The group is a mix 
 of GTA locals and newcomers to Toronto from within Canada and abroad.\n\nA
 ttendance numbers on Meetup don't reflect our actual event attendance - we
  typically have 15-20 community members at each event. Large enough that t
 here's someone new to meet but small enough that it's not overwhelming!\n\
 n***Learn more at our website [www.wildernessunion.com](https://www.wilder
 nessunion.com/)***
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/wildernessunion/events/314152930/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260406T200526Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260406T200526Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
